d the current crop of Republicans is no better at reading charts than George W was. I guess it's too h-a-r-d.  (obamasay.com) </p></div><div class="vine-p p-comment_MiniToolbox"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:74176584,&quot;threadId&quot;:&quot;3666295&quot;,&quot;contentId&quot;:&quot;16951837&quot;,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;chasboyle&quot;}"></div><ul class="list"><li class="box votes"><div class="label">2 votes</div></li></ul></div><img class="replybutton" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/b_reply_mini.gif" width="35" height="12" alt="Reply" /><span class="commentdate"><a href="#c74176584" title="Link to this comment">#7</a> - Wed Feb 13, 2013 4:26 PM EST</span><div class="clearfix"></div><div class="commentcontainer"><span></span></div></div></div></div><div class="vine-p p-comment_Comment showAvatars commentbody " id="c74176685"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:74176685,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;chrisboese&quot;,&quot;authorDisplayName&quot;:&quot;Chris Boese&quot;}"></div><div class="c_author"><div class="normal"><a href="http://chrisboese.newsvine.com/"><img class="comment_author_avatar" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/blank.gif" data-avatar_src="http://m.static.newsvine.com/servista/imagesizer?file=chrisboeseAF00623D-94A0-E429-55B5-A2D37774E86B.jpg&width=60" width="35" height="35" alt="Comment author avatar" data-is_default_avatar="false" /></a><a href="http://chrisboese.newsvine.com/">Chris Boese</a></div></div><div id="commentText_74176685" class="c_text"><div class="normal"><div class="commentSource"><p>Would be better shared with a more SEO- and human eyeballs-friendly decontextualized headline...</p>
<p>just sayin', y'all should know better. I fixed it when I shared it, but no one else will.</p></div><div class="vine-p p-comment_MiniToolbox"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:74176685,&quot;threadId&quot;:&quot;3666295&quot;,&quot;contentId&quot;:&quot;16951837&quot;,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;chrisboese&quot;}"></div><ul class="list"><li class="box votes"><div class="label">1 vote</div></li></ul></div><img class="replybutton" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/b_reply_mini.gif" width="35" height="12" alt="Reply" /><span class="commentdate"><a href="#c74176685" title="Link to this comment">#8</a> - Wed Feb 13, 2013 4:29 PM EST</span><div class="clearfix"></div><div class="commentcontainer"><span></span></div></div></div></div><div class="vine-p p-comment_Comment showAvatars commentbody " id="c74182711"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:74182711,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;meddlingmonk&quot;,&quot;authorDisplayName&quot;:&quot;MeddlingMonk&quot;}"></div><div class="c_author"><div class="normal"><a href="http://meddlingmonk.newsvine.com/"><img class="comment_author_avatar" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/blank.gif" data-avatar_src="http://m.static.newsvine.com/servista/imagesizer?file=meddlingmonk23DE183B-C814-28CA-A930-EBE95749D42A.uncropped.jpg&width=60" width="35" height="35" alt="Comment author avatar" data-is_default_avatar="false" /></a><a href="http://meddlingmonk.newsvine.com/">MeddlingMonk</a></div></div><div id="commentText_74182711" class="c_text"><div class="normal"><div class="commentSource"><p>It's not as if Republicans actually gave monkey's about the debt or deficit. What they do care deeply about is fearmongering about the debt and deficit as a means to eliminating all social programs.</p></div><div class="vine-p p-comment_MiniToolbox"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:74182711,&quot;threadId&quot;:&quot;3666295&quot;,&quot;contentId&quot;:&quot;16951837&quot;,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;meddlingmonk&quot;}"></div><ul class="list"></ul></div><img class="replybutton" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/b_reply_mini.gif" width="35" height="12" alt="Reply" /><span class="commentdate"><a href="#c74182711" title="Link to this comment">#9</a> - Wed Feb 13, 2013 8:33 PM EST</span><div class="clearfix"></div><div class="commentcontainer"><span></span></div></div></div></div><div class="vine-p p-comment_Comment showAvatars commentbody " id="c74184632"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:74184632,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;miracle&quot;,&quot;authorDisplayName&quot;:&quot;Miracle&quot;}"></div><div class="c_author"><div class="normal"><a href="http://miracle.newsvine.com/"><img class="comment_author_avatar" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/blank.gif" data-avatar_src="http://m.static.newsvine.com/servista/imagesizer?file=miracleEB60B15A-1B73-210D-C05D-B595BA54649A.jpg&width=60" width="35" height="35" alt="Comment author avatar" data-is_default_avatar="false" /></a><a href="http://miracle.newsvine.com/">Miracle</a></div></div><div id="commentText_74184632" class="c_text"><div class="normal"><div class="commentSource"><p>The thing is, a double-dip recession heading into the mid-terms would be just what the DC Republicans ordered. Of course the DC Republicans would never intentionally tank the economy for political benefit.</p></div><div class="vine-p p-comment_MiniToolbox"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:74184632,&quot;threadId&quot;:&quot;3666295&quot;,&quot;contentId&quot;:&quot;16951837&quot;,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;miracle&quot;}"></div><ul class="list"></ul></div><img class="replybutton" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/b_reply_mini.gif" width="35" height="12" alt="Reply" /><span class="commentdate"><a href="#c74184632" title="Link to this comment">#10</a> - Wed Fe